sudo apt install docker-compose
 
 docker-compose.yml : is the file listed all the service like (web, database, messageing)
 
 ====================================
  docker-compose.yml ->
 ================================ 
  services:
				web:
					image: "paramanandapati/webimage"
				database: 
					image: "mongodb
				messageing:
					image: "redis:alpin"
					
===================================
docker-compose up
				